-- FDA says five deaths may be related to Monster Energy drink
-- 
-- Mon Oct 22, 2012 3:46pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/10/22/us-usa-fda-monster-idUSBRE89L1CE20121022

 

 (Reuters) - The U.S. Food and Drug Administration said on Monday that it has received reports of five deaths and a heart attack since 2009 that may be associated with Monster Energy Drink. 
 (Reporting by  Michele Gershberg ; Editing by  Gary Hill )